  "title": "Incredibly Energizing Northern Thai Morning Glory Curry",
  "description": "A savory and shaggy Northern Thai dish featuring morning glory, perfect for a energizing meal. This satvik-friendly curry is made with poached morning glory and a blend of spices.",
