      "amount": "1/2 teaspoon"
    },
    {
      "name": "lemon juice",
      "amount": "1 tablespoon"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Poach the morning glory in boiling water for 2 minutes, then drain and set aside.",
    "Heat the oil in a large pan over medium heat.",
    "Add the onion, garlic, and ginger to the pan and saute until the onion is translucent.",
    "Add the curry paste to the pan and stir for 1 minute.",
    "Pour in the coconut milk and bring the mixture to a simmer.",
    "Add the poached morning glory, salt, pepper, and lemon juice to the pan and stir to combine.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and let the curry simmer for 10 minutes.",
    "Taste and adjust the seasoning as needed.",
    "Serve the curry hot, garnished with fresh herbs if desired."
